QuestData.Title: Shrieker Soul
QuestData.Description: <The Shrieker Soul is swift and fierce. The shape of the veil shrieker will be yours to call upon.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Shrieker Soul to Lady Muunn in the Heart of the Forest.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Bring the Shrieker Soul to Lady Muunn in the Heart of the Forest.
QuestData.RewardText: The shape of the veil shrieker is now yours to use if you choose.
